---
title: Duck and Double-Berry Sauce with Roasted Squash and Sweet Potato Mash
description: Duck loves a sweet companion and we've coupled it here with a lovely berry sauce. Butternut squash and sweet potatoes are roasted before getting mashed, for extra flavour from caramelization!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/canard-aux-petits-fruits-f1f40a97.jpg
